Please check the comments at the top of each file for the license. They
are usually one of the following:

* The FreeBSD Documentation License, for documentation;
* The 3-clause BSD License, for core utilities;
* The GNU General Public License, version 3 or any later version,
  for Makefiles and extra utilities.

The license texts are included in the source tree as COPYING.FBDL,
COPYING.3BSD, and COPYING.GPLv3.
